summary: An ordinance authorizing the execution of a contract with King County Fire Protection District No. 5 including the transfer to the City of all property of said District, the assumption by the City of all existing liabilities of the District, the furnishing by the City of certain fire protection to that portion of the District outside of the city and for payment therefor by the District, and the continued existence of the District for certain purposes; and repealing Ordinance No. 83451.
